title: Is This Vaccine Actually Causing The Condition it's 'Protecting' Against?
cleaned_text:
Stay connected to our guests and get special offers with our free email newsletter! http://www.ihealthtube.com/content/newsletter

Dr. Stephanie Seneff discusses vaccines, and in particular, the HPV vaccine. She talks about what she believes could be a real and serious side effect of the vaccine and why it may make people think a little more about a number of other vaccines!
